12 Developer API
****************

Use public ‘org-comments-*’ functions for package integration.
Functions with an ‘org-comments--’ prefix are private implementation
details and should not be called by backend packages.

   Important extension areas:

   • backend registration in ‘org-comments-backend.el’;
   • UI adapter variables in ‘org-comments-ui.el’ and panel action
     modules;
   • collaboration normalization in ‘org-comments-collaboration.el’;
   • explicit migration helpers in ‘org-comments-migrate.el’.


