13.1 No comments appear
=======================

Check that the source buffer is visiting a file and that the sibling
‘.comments.org’ file exists.  Local sidecars are file-backed.


File: org-comments.info,  Node: Legacy sidecar error,  Next: Remote operation is unsupported,  Prev: No comments appear,  Up: Troubleshooting

13.2 Legacy sidecar error
=========================

If collection reports legacy metadata, run ‘M-x
org-comments-migrate-sidecar’ on the sidecar file and retry.


File: org-comments.info,  Node: Remote operation is unsupported,  Next: Info manual is missing,  Prev: Legacy sidecar error,  Up: Troubleshooting

13.3 Remote operation is unsupported
====================================

Backends advertise capabilities.  If a backend does not support push,
pull, sync, or remote open, the generic command reports a clear
unsupported operation error.


File: org-comments.info,  Node: Info manual is missing,  Prev: Remote operation is unsupported,  Up: Troubleshooting

13.4 Info manual is missing
===========================

Build the manual from the repository checkout:

     devenv -q shell -- docs:org-comments

   Then add the package ‘docs/’ directory to ‘Info-directory-list’ or
install the Info file into your site Info directory.


